                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Escape",
                                "alt": "Escape",
                                "game-obj": "Actions",
                                "aonid": 2296
                            }
                        ],
                        "text": "If the boggard guard hits a creature with their tongue, that creature becomes grabbed by the boggard. Unlike with a normal Grab, the creature is not immobilized, but it can't move beyond the reach of the boggard's tongue. The DC to Escape is 15, or a creature can sever the tongue by hitting AC 12 and dealing at least 1 slashing damage. Though this doesn't deal any damage to the boggard, it prevents them from using their tongue Strike again until they regrow their tongue, which takes a week."
